com.chipsandwaycool.servlet

接口 MadnessConstants

  • 所有超级接口:
    HTMLConstants
    所有已知实现类:
    EditPlayer, EditPlayerAction, EditTeams, EditTeamsAction, EditWinners, EditWinnersAction, EmailPicks, EmailScores, Home, Initialization, Instructions, Login, MadnessServlet, MadnessWriter, MadnessWriterSkin1, Picks, PicksAction, PicksCSV, Scoreboard

    public interface MadnessConstants
extends HTMLConstants
    This interface defines various constant values needed throughout this servlet UI. I like to access such constants by "implementing" the interface, which obviates having class-name references everywhere. Much cleaner!
